# Codebase Architecture

## Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript
- Convex (backend/database)
- Clerk (authentication)
- Stripe (payments)
- TailwindCSS + Radix UI
- Sentry (monitoring)

## Structure
- `/app` - Next.js pages (App Router)
- `/components` - React components
- `/convex` - Backend functions and schema
- `/lib` - Utility functions
- `/utils` - Additional utilities
- `/hooks` - Custom React hooks

## Development
- `pnpm run dev` - Start frontend + backend
- `pnpm run dev:frontend` - Next.js only
- `pnpm run dev:backend` - Convex only

# Testing

## Unit Tests (Vitest)
- `pnpm test` - Interactive mode
- `pnpm test:run` - Single run
- `pnpm test:watch` - Watch mode
- `pnpm test:coverage` - With coverage
- `pnpm test:ui` - UI mode

## E2E Tests (Playwright)
- `pnpm pw:test` - Run tests
- `pnpm pw:test:ui` - UI mode
- `pnpm pw:test:debug` - Debug mode
- `pnpm pw:test:headed` - Headed mode
- `pnpm pw:report` - View report
- `pnpm pw:codegen` - Generate tests

# Linting

## ESLint
- `pnpm lint` - Run linter
- Config: Next.js + TypeScript rules
- File: `eslint.config.mjs`

## Build
- `pnpm build` - Production build
- `pnpm start` - Start production server
